    Summary

    Conscious Beauty at Ulta Beauty

    • Clean Ingredients
    • Cruelty Free

    There are always two sides to every lip story. Morphe's long-wearing Matte Liquid Lipstick goes on liquid-smooth and dries down to a velvety, matte finish. Just like that. Go on and mouth off in super-saturated color. All day. Every day.

    Details

    Benefits

    • Long-wearing & kiss-proof
    • Velvety, matte finish
    • Super-saturated color

    Ingredients

    Isododecane, Mica, Synthetic Beeswax, Trimethylsiloxysilicate, Dimethicone, Petrolatum, Polybutene, Trihydroxystearin, Flavor (Aroma), Cyclopentasiloxane, Silica, Disteardimonium Hectorite, Propylene Carbonate, Benzyl Benzoate, Cinnamal, Tocopheryl Acetate, Cucumis Sativus (Cucumber) Fruit Extract, Chamomilla Recutita Flower Extract, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Extract, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin. May Contain/Peut Contenir (+/-): Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891), Iron Oxides (CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499), Red 6 Lake (CI 15850), Yellow 5 (CI 19140), Manganese Violet (CI 77742).
